text:
Uh-oh, uh-oh, I can't be late anymore...
I'm off to the meeting...!

Um, the table...
...Can I tidy it up?

Oh... sorry
for leaving it messy...

Pens, documents, and stuff,
where should I put them?

For now, it's fine on that shelf over there!
I'll put them back in the right place later.

Sorry for the rush!
I'll thank you when I get back...!
